episodes.title: Here we go again!
episodes.description:
They are going to start coming for me so hard. You know, like cult stew when people speak out against them. Every time.


 My definition of a cult: 
1. The charismatic leader (& their skinny white woman) 
2. Worldview shift that brings you under the sacred assumption
3. The transcendent mission 
4. Self-sacrifice of members
5. Limits access to outside world
6. Distinguishable vernacular
7. Us versus them mentality
8. Exploits members labor
9. High entrance & exit costs 
10. Ends justify the means mentality

episodes.title: How I taught my husband about male privilege
episodes.description:
Before you say yes, please remember women couldn’t be military pilots in 1989

 My definition of a cult: 
1. The charismatic leader (& their skinny white woman) 
2. Worldview shift that brings you under the sacred assumption
3. The transcendent mission 
4. Self-sacrifice of members
5. Limits access to outside world
6. Distinguishable vernacular
7. Us versus them mentality
8. Exploits members labor
9. High entrance & exit costs 
10. Ends justify the means mentality
